   hello love...

   Welcome! I'm Bri! Accidental home cook. Lover of gathering people
   around a table over a meal. Author of Come & Eat (September 2017). What
   I really want is to pull out a chair for you at my table. But until
   then, I hope you stay awhile and enjoy my stories + recipes!

